data.description: Live just outside of Omaha on a double lot with fruit producing trees, chickens (optional) and easy place to park your boat, camper or RV! This beautifully maintained old world home is everything you need. 9ft ceilings on main level, original trim work and doors, spacious living and formal dining room. Huge Primary Bedroom on main floor with 2 closet spaces. The second bedroom on main floor. Second story of the home offers a loft perfect for a home office, 3rd bedroom with a conjoining 4th bedroom, ample closet space, along with a 3/4 bathroom. The detached garage has been remodeled inside and has a new 50 amp panel with a 30amp outlet for a RV. Propane is rented. HVAC is newer. Electrical panel inside home has been updated.
